posts.caption:
Recip for happyness (1-Person):

- Tell yourself every time the Truth
- head up your inner Dialog like with your best friend
- Tell your mirror image that you love it.
- be nice to yourself
- take care of yourself
- listen to your gut feeling
- just always do things, that is good for your soul (dont worry, just do it)
- Let your inner child out from time to time
- shed tears if you have to.
- be your own superhero (There is no Hero which saves you)
And the most important thing: you have to be loyal to yourself.
